Prepare Fast Chicken Soup Base. Bring to a simmer. Add these, then simmer until tender, 10-20 minutes: 1 9-ounce package refrigerated small cheese tortellini; 1 14.5-ounce can diced tomatoes; 2 medium zucchini, diced; 1 tsp. dried basil. Before removing from heat, stir in: 1/2 cup chopped fresh parsley. Final touch: Add salt and pepper, to taste.